Hi Trigger➛Check App Table Record➛Patient Name,

We regret to inform you that based on your laboratory results, you tested POSITIVE for SARS CoV-2 (causative agent of COVID 19).

The test was performed last Trigger➛Check App Table Record➛Date and Time Collected and was processed Trigger➛Check App Table Record➛Date and Time Processed.

We urge you to stay at home and quarantine for 14 days before you get tested again.

We hope that you will abide by our suggestion to be healthy and avoid the spread of the virus.

To see the full results of your laboratory test, please click the link of your record below:

 

Thank You.

Regards,

Service Hospital Co.

Hi Trigger➛Check App Table Record➛Patient Name,

We are happy to inform you that based on your laboratory results, you tested NEGATIVE for SARS CoV-2 (causative agent of COVID 19).

The test was performed last Trigger➛Check App Table Record➛Date and Time Collected and was processed Trigger➛Check App Table Record➛Date and Time Processed.

We urge you to still stay at home and avoid going out on unnecessary occasions to avoid getting the disease. We also suggest to wash your hands regularly and to eat healthy for prevention purposes.

We hope that you will abide by our suggestion to be healthy and to avoid the spread of the virus.

To see the full results of your laboratory test, please click the link of your record below:

Trigger➛Check App Table Record

Thank You.

Regards,

Service Hospital Co.
